fields.name: excluded
fields.descr: "True if the indicated class of service is excluded from the plan, missing or False indicated the service is included in the coverage."

fields.name: name
fields.descr: "A short name or tag for the benefit, for example MED01, or DENT2."

fields.name: description
fields.descr: "A richer description of the benefit, for example 'DENT2 covers 100% of basic, 50% of major but exclused Ortho, Implants and Costmetic services'."

fields.name: term
fields.descr: "The term or period of the values such as 'maximum lifetime benefit' or 'maximum annual vistis'."
